\subsection{Queue integration}{

Calling \verb{$enqueue()} adds this command at priority \code{160} and also
enqueues a \code{HomoplasyTreeScoresCommand} at priority \code{710} to compute
homoplasy scores after the search. This behaviour is inherited by
\link{ExtendedImpliedWeightingCommand}, which calls \verb{$enqueue()} on a
correctly configured \code{ImpliedWeightingCommand} before adding itself at
priority \code{230}.
}

\subsection{Role in the class hierarchy}{

\code{ImpliedWeightingCommand} and \link{ExtendedImpliedWeightingCommand} both inherit
from \link{AbstractImpliedWeightingCommand}, which defines the shared
\verb{$concavity_constant} active binding. \code{\link[=set_weighting]{set_weighting()}} handles the creation
and attachment of both commands transparently.
}
}
